            "id": "4577913",
            "title": "Lyft acquires Gett's UK business, adding London black cabs to portfolio",
            "description": "<html><body><p class=\"MsoNormal\" data-eci=\"true\">Lyft (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LYFT\" title=\"Lyft, Inc.\">LYFT</a></span></span>) has agreed to acquire Gett’s UK business, adding one of London’s leading black cab apps to its stable of holdings.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the addition of Gett’s black cabs, Lyft (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LYFT\" title=\"Lyft, Inc.\">LYFT</a>) now offers a comprehensive suite of ground transportation options, including private hires, bikes, and executive chauffeur services with its TBR Global Chauffeuring service.<span> This recent acquisition nearly doubles the number of rides on Lyft's (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LYFT\" title=\"Lyft, Inc.\">LYFT</a>) platform.  </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Additionally, through a partnership with Baidu (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BIDU\" title=\"Baidu, Inc.\">BIDU</a>), Lyft (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LYFT\" title=\"Lyft, Inc.\">LYFT</a>) will begin testing autonomous rides in London later this year.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">“With Gett, Lyft is expanding its coverage of London's full ground transport ecosystem,” said Jeremy Bird, EVP of Global Growth at Lyft. “This milestone reflects Lyft's commitment to the London market and our belief in its long-term potential.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The acquisition is expected to close in the coming weeks.</p>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/assets/og_image_1200-29b2bfe1a595477db6826bd2126c63ac2091efb7ec76347a8e7f81ba17e3de6c.png",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4577913-lyft-acquires-getts-uk-business-adding-london-black-cabs-to-portfolio",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 20:05:25",
            "source": "seekalpha",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
