            "title": "APi Group to acquire Onyx-Fire in $190M revenue deal",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>APi Group (APG) has <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20484855-api-group-to-acquire-onyx-fire-protection-services-inc\">agreed to acquire</a> Onyx-Fire Protection Services from funds managed by Blackstone Tactical Opportunities.</li>\n<li>The deal is expected to close in Q2 2026.</li>\n<li>Onyx-Fire generates over 50% of its revenue from inspection, service, and monitoring.</li>\n<li>The company is projected to contribute about $190M in annual revenue to APi.</li>\n<li>Onyx-Fire is expected to be accretive to APi’s “10/16/60+” shareholder value strategy due to its margins and asset-light model.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
